{"tid":2463789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Hugo Boss撤支持新疆棉帖文　改稱不容忍強迫勞動","createTime":"2021-03-27T03:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T03:42:00.000Z","uid":3801,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8a2bd0de75f498259a400dd273db1544430a1b","tid":2463789,"uid":3801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:39:22.000Z","msg":"內地新疆棉風波持續擴大，德國服裝品牌Hugo Boss亦受到波及。Hugo Boss前晚一度在微博表態支持新疆棉，會繼續採購，但帖文已被刪除，今早貼出最新的英文版聲明，指不容忍強迫勞力，目前沒有採購來自新疆地區的原料，會仔細檢查所有供應商是否符合相關的價值觀和標準，又強調珍惜與中國合作伙伴的友誼。多名內地藝人隨即宣布終止與Hugo Boss的合作。<br />\n有傳媒發現Hugo Boss對新疆棉的立場反覆，前日在微博表態支持，但以德語發出的新聞稿則表示致力尊重人權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪蝦班支支唔識英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee34fa8462ceedd4101d9b80d96e54b2014105d","tid":2463789,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:40:34.000Z","msg":"Hugo boss 二戰時都幫納粹做軍服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個字型！"},{"pid":"da66ca47182f8366dffd0df0b39f3ea7889144ef","tid":2463789,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"Xitler 觸及德國人神經<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcda659f894429d9784e776c364e01e95649a46","tid":2463789,"uid":173060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:41:16.000Z","msg":"擺明係d 支那仔無問過總公司就自己出文支持啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452d8ceba44b38f5b8425f0059403c16a83f6b9e","tid":2463789,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:41:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0uO9crTIJ8M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0uO9crTIJ8M&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWmDcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=05c8bddc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0uO9crTIJ8M</a><br />\n老燒哩段應該全部公開"},{"pid":"46f06b0b478e42bcb0eadab4b25445effbdb28e0","tid"